column1: Sessions: Standard Session : Book Sessions: The total price is calculated as $250 instead of $650 when no additional subject is chosen
column25:
*Steps to reproduce:*
 # Go to " [https://photostudio.demohoster.com/sessions/book/3] "
 # Log in to this system
 # Click on Sessions 
 # Click on book now under the standard sessions
 # Select additional  subject none is selected by default
 # Click on Book button
 # Observed the total price on the Book information page
 # Back to the previous page and select 1 additional subjects
 # Observed the total price

*Actual Result:* The total price is calculated as $250 instead of $650 when no additional subject is chosen.

*Expected Result:* The total price should be calculated at $650 when no additional values are selected.

*Additional Information:* When the additional subject is chosen also the calculation is wrong. Because the start price is wrong. Total price calculation rule:

Total price= start price +55*<selected value from the dropdown>

For Standard sessions  $650+$55*<selected value from the dropdown>

column1: Sessions: Mini Studio Session: Book Session: $5 is deducted from the total price when additional subjects 1 is selected and a session is booked
column25:
Steps to reproduce:
 # Go to " [https://photostudio.demohoster.com/sessions/book] "
 # Log in to this system
 # Click on Session and then click on mini studio session book now button
 # Select additional subjects 1
 # click on the Book button
 # Observed the Total price
 # $5 is deducted from the total price

*Actual Result:* $5 is deducted from the total price when additional subjects 1 is selected and a session is booked 

*Expected Result:* When an additional subject is selected the price of an additional subject $55 will be added to the total price. For Mini studio session starting price $250 additional subject 1 =$55. The total price will be $250+$55=$305

*Addition Information:* This issue is the same for 2 to 10 additional subjects. when 2 additional subjects are selected deduct $10, 7 additional subjects deduct $35, and 10 additional subjects $50 is deducted from the total price.
